So where does the data get downloaded on to the local filesystem and what data ends up to the image?

Patch Set 1:

> So where does the data get downloaded on to the local filesystem
 > and what data ends up to the image?

Hi Erno,

AFAIK, If node_staging_uri is not set explicitly in glance-direc.conf then it us takin default value i.e./tmp/staging instead. As you see the logs it's breaking due to seperator is not initialised properly.
